name: Travel
description:
The next morning, Gobo the frog took me to many attractions in the city. He told me that he works as a keeper at the shrine. At the weekend, he likes to travel around places which are not busy because he found another kind of enjoyment from peaceful and calm places.

In addition, he also does any part-time jobs if those jobs involve "water" for example, freediving to collect clam, cleaning fish tanks, and maguro fishing in the ocean.
